  "articleBody": "<!-- FR:158 JA:126  -->\n\n<article>\n\n<hgroup>\n<h1 class=\"green\"><ruby style=\"color:#555;\">Vendôme&nbsp;<wbr>Square<rt style=\"color:#999;font-size:0.95rem;\">place&nbsp;<wbr>Vendôme</rt></ruby></h1>\n<h2 class=\"green\">in the <abbr title=\"seventeenth\">17<sup style=\"color:#3d8b3d;\">th</sup></abbr> century</h2>\n</hgroup>\n\n<figure>\n  <picture><source media=\"(min-width: 959px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-280.webp 280w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-380.webp 380w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-480.webp 480w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-640.webp 640w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome_700x507.webp 700w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-focus-280.webp 280w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-focus-380.webp 380w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-focus-480.webp 480w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-focus-640.webp 640w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-focus_700x415.webp 700w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 959px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-280.jpg 280w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-380.jpg 380w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-480.jpg 480w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-640.jpg 640w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome_700x507.jpg https://francois-vidit.com700w\"><img src=\"/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-focus_700x415.jpg\" alt=\"La Place Vendôme à Paris, en 1734\" title=\"La Place Vendôme à Paris, en 1734\" class=\"class-diane-img\" width=\"700\" height=\"415\" loading=\"eager\" decoding=\"async\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-focus-280.jpg 280w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-focus-380.jpg 380w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-focus-480.jpg 480w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-focus-640.jpg 640w,\n  /docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-focus_700x415.jpg 700w\"></picture><figcaption><ruby lang=\"en\">Vendôme&nbsp;Square<rt style=\"color:#999;\" lang=\"fr\">place&nbsp;Vendôme</rt></ruby> in Paris according to the <ruby lang=\"en\">Turgot&nbsp;Plan<rt style=\"color:#999;\" lang=\"fr\">Plan&nbsp;de&nbsp;Turgot</rt></ruby> in <time datetime=\"1734\">1734</time>.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n<h2 class=\"green\">Vendôme Square in the Paris of the <abbr title=\"seventeenth\">17<sup style=\"color:#3d8b3d;\">th</sup></abbr> century</h2>\n\n<div class=\"notices green\">\n<p>The <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Place_Vendôme\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Place_Vendôme\"><ruby>Vendôme&nbsp;Square<rp>(</rp><rt>place&nbsp;Vendôme</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></a> had a very different face before the opening of the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rue_de_Rivoli\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rue_de_Rivoli\"><ruby>Rivoli&nbsp;Street<rp>(</rp><rt>rue&nbsp;de&nbsp;Rivoli</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></a> made in only <time datetime=\"1801\">1801</time>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>The square was first constructed in a square form.</p>\n<p>This form is considered too rigid; in <time datetime=\"1700\">1700</time>, part of the facades was torn down and then rebuilt, in 1701, in the present octagonal form. They are the work of the architect <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jules_Hardouin-Mansart\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jules_Hardouin-Mansart\">Jules-Hardouin MANSART</a>.</p>\n<p>Looking closely at the <time datetime=\"1734\">1734</time> <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Turgot_map_of_Paris\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Turgot_map_of_Paris\">Turgot Plan</a>, the place appears to be much calmer than actually:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>on the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tuileries_Garden\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tuileries_Garden\">Tuileries</a> side, The <a href=\"https://www.google.fr/maps/place/Rue de Castiglione, 75001 Paris/@48.8659408,2.3257194,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m8!1m2!2m1!1scastiglione street paris!3m4!1s0x47e66e2de4cf6571:0xad54eb95ed09a09!8m2!3d48.8659408!4d2.3279081\" title=\"https://www.google.fr/maps/place/Rue+de+Castiglione,+75001+Paris/@48.8659408,2.3257194,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m8!1m2!2m1!1scastiglione+street+paris!3m4!1s0x47e66e2de4cf6571:0xad54eb95ed09a09!8m2!3d48.8659408!4d2.3279081\"><ruby>Castiglione&nbsp;Street<rp>(</rp><rt>rue&nbsp;de&nbsp;Castiglione</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></a> (<a href=\"#castiglione\"><abbr title=\"figure\">fig.</abbr> 1</a>),</li>\n  <li>on the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paris_Opera\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paris_Opera\">Opéra</a> side, the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rue_de_la_Paix,_Paris\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rue_de_la_Paix,_Paris\"><ruby>Paix&nbsp;Street<rp>(</rp><rt>rue&nbsp;de&nbsp;la&nbsp;Paix</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></a> in <a href=\"#paix\"><abbr title=\"figure\">fig.</abbr>&nbsp2</a>,\n  has not yet been pierced.</li>\n</ul>\n\n",
  "articleBody2": "<figure><picture><source media=\"(min-width: 959px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-280.webp 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-380.webp 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-480.webp 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-640.webp 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione_700x507.webp 700w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 959px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-280.jpg 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-380.jpg 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-480.jpg 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-640.jpg 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione_700x507.jpg 700w\"><source sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-focus-280.webp 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-focus-380.webp 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-focus-480.webp 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-focus-640.webp 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-focus_669x484.webp 669w\"><img id=\"castiglione\" src=\"/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-focus_700x415.jpg\" alt=\"La Place Vendôme à Paris, côté rue Castiglione, en 1734\" title=\"La Place Vendôme à Paris, côté rue Castiglione, en 1734\" class=\"class-diane-img\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-focus-280.jpg 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-focus-380.jpg 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-focus-480.jpg 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-focus-640.jpg 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-castiglione-focus_669x484.jpg 669w\"></picture><figcaption><b><abbr title=\"figure\">fig.</abbr>&nbsp1.</b> Prior to the puncture of <ruby lang=\"en\">Castiglione&nbsp;Street<rt style=\"color:#999;\" lang=\"fr\">rue&nbsp;de&nbsp;Castiglione</rt></ruby>, access from <ruby lang=\"en\">Saint-Honoré&nbsp;Street<rt style=\"color:#999;\" lang=\"fr\">rue&nbsp;Saint-Honoré</rt></ruby> in <time datetime=\"1734\">1734</time>.</figcaption></figure>\n\n<p>The access is only by:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rue_Saint-Honoré\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rue_Saint-Honoré\"><ruby>Saint-Honoré&nbsp;Street<rp>(</rp><rt>rue&nbsp;Saint-Honoré</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></a> on the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tuileries_Garden\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tuileries_Garden\">Tuileries</a> side (<a href=\"#castiglione\"><abbr title=\"figure\">fig.</abbr>&nbsp1</a> above),</li>\n  <li>and the <a href=\"https://www.google.fr/maps/place/Rue des Capucines, Paris/@48.8689074,2.3272296,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m8!1m2!2m1!1scapucines street paris!3m4!1s0x47e66e31789d3efd:0x1c0b307ea31b237e!8m2!3d48.8689074!4d2.3294183\" title=\"https://www.google.fr/maps/place/Rue+des+Capucines,+Paris/@48.8689074,2.3272296,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m8!1m2!2m1!1scapucines+street+paris!3m4!1s0x47e66e31789d3efd:0x1c0b307ea31b237e!8m2!3d48.8689074!4d2.3294183\"><ruby>Capucines&nbsp;Street<rp>(</rp><rt>rue&nbsp;des&nbsp;Capucines</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></a> on the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paris_Opera\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paris_Opera\">Opéra</a> side (<a href=\"#paix\"><abbr title=\"figure\">fig.</abbr>&nbsp2</a> below).  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<figure><picture><source media=\"(min-width: 959px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-280.webp 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-380.webp 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-480.webp 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-640.webp 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix_700x507.webp 700w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 959px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-280.jpg 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-380.jpg 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-480.jpg 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-640.jpg 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix_700x507.jpg 700w\"><source sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-focus-280.webp 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-focus-380.webp 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-focus-480.webp 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-focus-640.webp 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-focus_700x447.webp 700w\"><img id=\"paix\" src=\"/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-focus_700x415.jpg\" alt=\"La Place Vendôme à Paris, côté rue de la Paix, en 1734\" title=\"La Place Vendôme à Paris, côté rue de la Paix, en 1734\" class=\"class-diane-img\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-focus-280.jpg 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-focus-380.jpg 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-focus-480.jpg 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-focus-640.jpg 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-paix-focus_700x447.jpg 700w\"></picture><figcaption><b><abbr title=\"figure\">fig.</abbr>&nbsp2.</b> Prior to the puncture of <ruby lang=\"en\">Paix&nbsp;Street<rt style=\"color:#999;\" lang=\"fr\">rue&nbsp;de&nbsp;la&nbsp;Paix</rt></ruby>, access from <ruby lang=\"en\">Capucines&nbsp;Street<rt style=\"color:#999;\" lang=\"fr\">rue&nbsp;des&nbsp;Capucines</rt></ruby></figcaption></figure>\n\n",
  "articleBody3": "<p>It could not be passed through as since the <abbr title=\"nineteen\">19<sup>th</sup></abbr> century.</p>\n<p>On the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paris_Opera\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paris_Opera\"><ruby>Opera<rp>(</rp><rt>Opéra</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></a> side, at the location of the current <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rue_de_la_Paix,_Paris\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rue_de_la_Paix,_Paris\"><ruby>Paix&nbsp;Street<rp>(</rp><rt>rue&nbsp;de&nbsp;la&nbsp;Paix</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></a>, was the <a href=\"https://www.google.fr/maps/place/3 Rue de la Paix, 75002 Paris/@48.8686382,2.3282652,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x47e66e31a48a6115:0xf23e0c7b6c50cd93!8m2!3d48.8686382!4d2.3304539\" title=\"https://www.google.fr/maps/place/3+Rue+de+la+Paix,+75002+Paris/@48.8686382,2.3282652,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x47e66e31a48a6115:0xf23e0c7b6c50cd93!8m2!3d48.8686382!4d2.3304539\"><ruby>convent&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Capucines<rp>(</rp><rt>couvent&nbsp;des&nbsp;Capucines</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></a> (<a href=\"#couvent\"><abbr title=\"figure\">fig.</abbr>&nbsp3</a>).</p>\n\n<figure><picture><source media=\"(min-width: 959px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-280.webp 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-380.webp 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-480.webp 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-640.webp 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent_700x411.webp 700w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 959px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-280.jpg 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-380.jpg 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-480.jpg 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-640.jpg 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent_700x411.jpg 700w\"><source sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-focus-280.webp 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-focus-380.webp 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-focus-480.webp 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-focus-640.webp 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-focus_700x447.webp 700w\"><img id=\"couvent\" src=\"/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-focus_700x411.jpg\" alt=\"Le second couvent des Capucines, Place Vendôme à Paris, 1705\" title=\"Le second couvent des Capucines, Place Vendôme à Paris, 1705\" class=\"class-diane-img\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-focus-280.jpg 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-focus-380.jpg 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-focus-480.jpg 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-focus-640.jpg 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-couvent-focus_700x411.jpg 700w\"></picture><figcaption><b><abbr title=\"figure\">fig.</abbr>&nbsp3.</b> Prior to the puncture of <ruby lang=\"en\">Paix&nbsp;Street<rt style=\"color:#999;\" lang=\"fr\">rue&nbsp;de&nbsp;la&nbsp;Paix</rt></ruby>, the second <ruby lang=\"en\">Convent&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Capucines<rt style=\"color:#999;\" lang=\"fr\">couvent&nbsp;des&nbsp;Capucines</rt></ruby> dating of <time datetime=\"1705\">1705</time>.</figcaption></figure>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madame_de_Pompadour\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madame_de_Pompadour\">Madame de Pompadour</a> was buried, as was her mother and sister, in the church.</p>\n<p>In front, on the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paris_Opera\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paris_Opera\">Tuileries</a>' side, another portal, the portal of <a href=\"https://www.google.fr/maps/place/3 Rue de la Paix, 75002 Paris/@48.8686382,2.3282652,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x47e66e31a48a6115:0xf23e0c7b6c50cd93!8m2!3d48.8686382!4d2.3304539\" title=\"https://www.google.fr/maps/place/3+Rue+de+la+Paix,+75002+Paris/@48.8686382,2.3282652,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x47e66e31a48a6115:0xf23e0c7b6c50cd93!8m2!3d48.8686382!4d2.3304539\"><ruby>convent&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Capucines<rp>(</rp><rt>couvent&nbsp;des&nbsp;Capucines</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></a> was responding to it (<a href=\"#feuillants\"><abbr title=\"figure\">fig.</abbr>&nbsp4</a>).</p>\n\n",
  "articleBody4": "<figure><picture><source media=\"(min-width: 959px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-280.webp 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-380.webp 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-480.webp 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-640.webp 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants_700x419.webp 700w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 959px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-280.jpg 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-380.jpg 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-480.jpg 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-640.jpg 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants_700x419.jpg 700w\"><source sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-focus-280.webp 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-focus-380.webp 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-focus-480.webp 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-focus-640.webp 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-focus_700x438.webp 700w\"><img id=\"feuillants\" src=\"/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-focus_700x438.jpg\" alt=\"le portail du couvent des Feuillants, Place Vendôme à Paris, 1754\" title=\"le portail du couvent des Feuillants, Place Vendôme à Paris, 1754\" class=\"class-diane-img\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-focus-280.jpg 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-focus-380.jpg 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-focus-480.jpg 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-focus-640.jpg 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-feuillants-focus_700x438.jpg 700w\"></picture><figcaption><b><abbr title=\"figure\">fig.</abbr>&nbsp4.</b> Prior to the puncture of <ruby lang=\"en\">Castiglione&nbsp;Street<rt style=\"color:#999;\" lang=\"fr\">rue&nbsp;de&nbsp;Castiglione</rt></ruby>, the portal of <ruby lang=\"en\">convent&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Feuillants<rt style=\"color:#999;\" lang=\"fr\">couvent&nbsp;des&nbsp;Feuillants</rt></ruby> in <time datetime=\"1754\">1754</time>.</figcaption></figure>\n\n<p>In the center of the square, was erected, since <time datetime=\"1699\">1699</time>, the statue of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louis_XIV_of_France\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louis_XIV_of_France\">Louis XIV</a> called «Louis le Grand» (<a href=\"#statue\"><abbr title=\"figure\">fig.</abbr>&nbsp5</a>).</p>\n\n<figure><picture><source media=\"(min-width: 959px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-280.webp 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-380.webp 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-480.webp 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-640.webp 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue_700x1024.webp 700w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 959px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-280.jpg 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-380.jpg 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-480.jpg 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-640.jpg 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue_700x1024.jpg 700w\"><source sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-focus-280.webp 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-focus-380.webp 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-focus-480.webp 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-focus-640.webp 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-focus_700x875.webp 700w\"><img id=\"statue\" src=\"/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-focus_700x875.jpg\" alt=\"la statue de Louis Le Grand, Place Vendôme à Paris, 1699\" title=\"la statue de Louis Le Grand, Place Vendôme à Paris, 1699\" class=\"class-diane-img\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 98vw, (min-width: 959px) 50vw, 86vw\" srcset=\"\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-focus-280.jpg 280w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-focus-380.jpg 380w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-focus-480.jpg 480w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-focus-640.jpg 640w,\n/docs/place-vendome/place-vendome-statue-focus_700x875.jpg 700w\"></picture><figcaption><b><abbr title=\"figure\">fig.</abbr>&nbsp5.</b> in the middle of the square, the statue of Louis Le Grand in <time datetime=\"1699\">1699</time>.</figcaption></figure>\n\n<p>It is an impressive work by <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/François_Girardon\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/François_Girardon\">François GIRARDON</a> , which reaches, with its pedestal, a height of 17&nbspm high.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/French_Revolution\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/French_Revolution\"><ruby>Revolution<rp>(</rp><rt>Révolution</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></a> will destroy it but one of the huge feet of the king survived its melt and is exhibited at the Museum of History of the City of Paris, the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carnavalet_Museum\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carnavalet_Museum\"><ruby>Carnavalet&nbsp;Museum<rp>(</rp><rt>Musée&nbsp;Carnavalet</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></a>.</p>\n\n<aside>\n<div class=\"notices green\">\n<p>For more information on the work of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/François_Girardon\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/François_Girardon\">François GIRARDON</a>, consult its <a href=\"http://www.louvre.fr/en/oeuvre-notices/louis-xiv-horseback\" title=\"http://www.louvre.fr/en/oeuvre-notices/louis-xiv-horseback\">reference on the Louvre Museum site</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</aside>\n\n</article>"
}